  "text": "ii) University of Michigan [CITATION_1] ; Consists of 96 samples: 86 -primary adenocarcinoma (where 67 -stage I, nineteen -stage III), ten -non-neoplastic tissue. Each sample is presented by expression levels of 7,129 genes. The task was to detect adenocarcinoma.",
